story :
Teenage girl who fled from the Arabian Peninsula. Caught by police at the border for hiding something in his bag, he keeps a simurg which is a legendary bird from Iran. Due to her persistence in protecting the simurg, the bird finally took action and flapped its wings to bring out its power and protect it. This action gave the girl the strength to survive while protecting the earth from evil forces.
